#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Hitri vodnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new project"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novega projekta"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Kdenlive directory structure</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Struktura imenikov Kdenlive</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Kdenlive directory structure</para>"
msgstr "<para>Struktura imenikov Kdenlive</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is creating a new (empty) folder for our new project. I will "
"call it <filename>quickstart-tutorial/</filename> in this tutorial. Then get "
"some sample video clips, or download them from here:<ulink url=\"http://"
"granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar."
"bz2\">kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar.bz2</ulink> (7 "
"MB)<footnote><para>If you prefer Theora (which you probably don’t since Ogg "
"Video usually causes problems), you can alternatively download <ulink url="
"\"http://granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-"
"ogv.tar.bz2\">kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2</ulink>.</para></"
"footnote>, and extract them to &eg; a <filename>quickstart-tutorial/Videos/</"
"filename> subfolder inside the project folder."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je ustvarjanje nove (prazne) mape za naš novi projekt. V tej "
"vadnici ga bom imenoval <filename>quickstart-tutorial/</filename> v tej "
"vadnici. Nato pridobite nekaj vzorčnih video posnetkov ali jih prenesite od "
"tukaj:kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar.bz2 (7 MB)<footnote><para>Če vam "
"je ljubša Theora (kar verjetno ne, saj Ogg Video običajno povzroča težave), "
"lahko alternativno prenesete <ulink url=\"http://granjow.net/uploads/"
"kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2\">kdenlive-"
"tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2.,</ulink></para></footnote> in jih "
"izvlečete v &eg; <filename>hitro vadnico / videoposnetke /</filename> "
"podmapo v mapi projekta<ulink url=\"http://granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/"
"manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar.bz2\">.</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image on the left shows the suggested directory structure: Each project "
"has its own directory, with video files in the <filename>Videos</filename> "
"subdirectory, audio files in the <filename>Audio</filename> directory, &etc; "
"(<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Projects_and_Files#File_Structure\">read more</ulink>)"
msgstr ""
"Slika na levi prikazuje predlagano strukturo imenika: Vsak projekt ima svoj "
"imenik, z video datotekami v podimeniku <filename>Videoposnetki</filename> , "
"zvočnimi datotekami v imeniku <filename>Zvok</filename> itn. (<ulink url="
"\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Projects_and_Files#File_Structure\">preberite več</ulink>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(The tutorial from now on assumes that you use the sample videos provided, "
"but it works with any.)"
msgstr ""
"(Vadnica od zdaj naprej predvideva, da uporabljate navedene vzorčne "
"videoposnetke, vendar deluje s poljubnimi.)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New Project dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno Nov projekt</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>New Project dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno Nov projekt</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kdenlive; and create a new project (<menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Odprite &kdenlive; in ustvarite nov projekt (<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the previously created project folder (<filename>quickstart-tutorial/"
"</filename>) and select an appropriate project profile. The video files "
"provided above are 720p, 23.98 fps.<footnote><para><ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/720p\">720</ulink> is the video height, p stands for "
"<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_scan\">progressive "
"scan</ulink> in contrast to <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Interlaced_video\">interlaced video</ulink>, and the fps number denotes the "
"number of full frames per second.</para></footnote> If you are using your "
"own files and don’t know which one to use, &kdenlive; will suggest an "
"appropriate one when the first clip is added <footnote><para>Provided "
"Configure Kdenlive Settings under <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/Settings_Menu/Configure_Kdenlive#Misc"
"\">Misc</ulink> is set to <emphasis>Check if first added clip matches "
"project profile</emphasis></para></footnote> , so you can leave the field on "
"whatever it is."
msgstr ""
"Izberite predhodno ustvarjeno mapo projekta (<filename>quickstart-tutorial/</"
"filename>) in izberite ustrezen profil projekta. Zgoraj navedene video "
"datoteke so 720p, 23,98 sl/s. <footnote><para><ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/720p\">720</ulink> je višina videa, p pomeni <ulink url="
"\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_scan\">progresivno skeniranje</"
"ulink> v nasprotju s <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Interlaced_video\">prepletenim videom</ulink>, številka sl/s pa označuje "
"število celih sličic na sekundo.</para></footnote> Če uporabljate svoje "
"datoteke in ne veste, katero uporabiti, &kdenlive; bo predlagal ustrezno, ko "
"bo dodan prvi posnetek<footnote><para>Ponujena nastavitev pod Prilagodi "
"Kdenlive pod <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"Kdenlive/Manual/Settings_Menu/Configure_Kdenlive#Misc\">Razno</ulink> je "
"nastavljena na <emphasis>Preveri, ali se prvi dodani posnetek ujema s "
"profilom projekta</emphasis></para></footnote> , tako da lahko pustite polje "
"na poljubni nastavitvi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding clips"
msgstr "Dodajanje posnetkov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Project Bin: Adding video clips</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Projektna posoda: dodajanje videoposnetkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Project Bin: Adding video clips</para>"
msgstr "<para>Projektna posoda: dodajanje videoposnetkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that the project is ready, let’s start adding some clips (&ie; the ones "
"you downloaded). This works via the <emphasis>Project Bin widget</emphasis>; "
"a click on the <guilabel>Add Clip</guilabel> icon <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-add-clip.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> directly opens the file dialog, a click on "
"the small arrow shows a list of additional clip types that can be added as "
"well. Video clips, audio clips, images, and other &kdenlive; projects can be "
"added via the default <guilabel>Add Clip</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko je projekt pripravljen, začnimo dodajati nekaj posnetkov (&ie;. "
"Tiste, ki ste jih prenesli). To deluje prek <emphasis>pripomočka Project "
"Bin</emphasis>; s klikom na ikono <guilabel>Dodaj izrezek</guilabel> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-add-clip.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> neposredno odpre "
"pogovorno okno datoteke, s klikom na majhno puščico se prikaže seznam "
"dodatnih vrst posnetkov, ki jih je mogoče tudi dodati. Videoposnetke, zvočne "
"posnetke, slike in druge &kdenlive; projekte lahko dodate prek privzetega "
"pogovornega okna <guilabel>Dodaj izrezek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Kdenlive window with the tutorial files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno Kdenlive z datotekami vadnic</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Kdenlive window with the tutorial files</para>"
msgstr "<para>Okno Kdenlive z datotekami vadnic</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After loading the clips, &kdenlive; will look similar to this. On the top "
"left there is the already known project tree. Right of it are the monitors "
"that show video; The clip monitor displays video from the original clips, "
"the project monitor shows how the output video will look, with all effects, "
"transitions, &etc; applied. The third, also very important, item is the "
"timeline (below the monitors): This is the place where the video clips will "
"be edited. There are two different types of tracks, Video and Audio. Video "
"tracks can contain any kind of clip, audio tracks as well – but when "
"dropping a video file to the audio track, only the audio will be used."
msgstr ""
"Po nalaganju posnetkov bo &kdenlive; videti podobno temu. Zgoraj levo je že "
"znano drevo projekta. Desno od tega sta ogleda, ki prikazujeta video; ogled "
"posnetka prikazuje video iz izvirnih posnetkov, ogled projekta prikazuje, "
"kako bo izgledal izhodni video z vsemi učinki in prehodi. Tretja, prav tako "
"zelo pomembna postavka je časovnica (pod ogledoma): to je mesto, kjer bodo "
"video posnetki montirani. Obstajata dve različni vrsti stez, video in "
"zvočne. Video posnetki lahko vsebujejo vse vrste posnetkov, tudi zvočne "
"posnetke - toda pri spuščanju video datoteke na zvočni posnetek bo "
"uporabljen samo zvok."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Saving a Kdenlive project</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Shranjevanje projekta Kdenlive</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Saving a Kdenlive project</para>"
msgstr "<para>Shranjevanje projekta Kdenlive</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let’s save the work via <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This saves our project, &ie; "
"where we placed the clips on the timeline, which effects we applied, and so "
"on. It can <emphasis>not</emphasis> be played.<footnote><para>To be correct, "
"it <emphasis>can</emphasis> be played using <varname>melt yourproject."
"kdenlive</varname>, but this is not the way you would want to present your "
"final video since it is (most likely) too slow. Additionally, it only works "
"if melt is installed.</para></footnote> The process of creating the final "
"video is called <emphasis>Rendering</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Shranimo delo prek <menuchoice><guimenu>datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>shrani</guimenuitem>.</menuchoice> To prihrani naš projekt, "
"&ie; kam smo postavili posnetke na časovnico, katere učinke smo uporabili in "
"tako naprej. <emphasis>Ni</emphasis> ga mogoče igrati. <footnote><para>Če "
"želite biti pravilni, ga <emphasis>lahko</emphasis> predvajate s "
"<varname>taljenjem yourproject.kdenlive</varname>, vendar to ni način, kako "
"bi želeli predstaviti svoj končni video, saj je (najverjetneje) prepočasen. "
"Poleg tega deluje le, če je nameščena talina.</para></footnote> Postopek "
"ustvarjanja končnega videoposnetka se imenuje <emphasis>upodabljanje</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Časovnica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Timeline\">Timeline section of the manual</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Glej tudi <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Timeline\">razdelek priročnika Časovnica</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now comes the actual editing. Project clips are combined to the final result "
"on the timeline. They get there by drag and drop: Drag some Napoli (assuming "
"you are using the files provided above, as in the rest of this quick start "
"tutorial; If not, please make sure your screen is waterproof, and perhaps "
"tomatoproof) from the project tree, and drop it onto the first track in the "
"timeline."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj prihaja dejanska montaža. Posnetki projekta so združeni s končnim "
"rezultatom na časovnici. Do tja pridejo tako, da jih povlečete in spustite: "
"povlecite nekaj Napolija (ob predpostavki, da uporabljate zgoraj navedene "
"datoteke, kot v preostalem delu te vadnice za hitri začetek; če ne, se "
"prepričajte, da je vaš zaslon vodoodporen in morda odporen na paradižnik) iz "
"drevesa projekta in ga spustite na prvo stezo na časovnici."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>First clips in the timeline</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prvi posnetki na časovnici</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>First clips in the timeline</para>"
msgstr "<para>Prvi posnetki na časovnici</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since some cutlery is needed as well, grab the spoon clip and drop it on the "
"first track as well. Then drag the Napoli to the beginning of the timeline "
"(otherwise the rendered video would start with some seconds of plain black), "
"and the Spoon right after the Napoli, such that it looks like in the image "
"on the left. (Where I have zoomed in with <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Wheel</"
"keycap></keycombo>.)"
msgstr ""
"Ker je potrebno tudi nekaj jedilnega pribora, zgrabite posnetek z žlico in "
"ga spustite tudi na prvo stezo. Nato povlecite Napoli na začetek časovnice "
"(sicer bi se izrisani video začel z nekaj sekundami navadne črne barve) in "
"žlico takoj za Napolijem, tako da je videti kot na sliki na levi (kje sem "
"povečal s kombinacijo <keycombo>krmilka<keycap>kolešček miške</keycap></"
"keycombo>.)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Timeline cursor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kazalec časovnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Timeline cursor</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kazalec časovnice</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result can already be previewed by pressing <keycap>Space</keycap> (or "
"the <guilabel>Play</guilabel> button in the project monitor). You will see "
"the Napoli directly followed by a Spoon. If the timeline cursor is not at "
"the beginning, the project monitor will start playing somewhere in the "
"middle; you can move it by dragging it either on the timeline ruler or in "
"the project monitor. If you prefer keyboard shortcuts, <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> does the same for the monitor that is "
"activated. (Select the <guilabel>Project Monitor</guilabel> if it is not "
"selected yet before using the shortcut.)"
msgstr ""
"Rezultat si lahko že ogledate tako, da pritisnete <keycap>preslednico</"
"keycap> (ali gumb <guilabel>Predvajaj</guilabel> v ogledu projektau). Napoli "
"boste videli neposredno, ki mu bo sledila žlica. Če kazalec časovnice ni na "
"začetku, bo ogled projekta začel predvajati nekje na sredini; premaknete ga "
"lahko tako, da ga povlečete na ravnilu časovnice ali v ogledu projekta. Če "
"imate raje bližnjice na tipkovnici, <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Home</keycap></"
"keycombo> naredi enako za okno ogleda, ki je aktivirano ( <guilabel>Izberite "
"okno projekta</guilabel> , če še ni izbrano, preden uporabite bližnjico)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Resize marker</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Označevalnik spreminjanja velikosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Resize marker</para>"
msgstr "<para>Označevalnik spreminjanja velikosti</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since after eating comes playing, there is a Billiards clip. Add it to the "
"timeline as well. For the first 1.5 seconds nothing happens in the clip, so "
"it should perhaps be <guilabel>cut</guilabel> to avoid the video becoming "
"boring. An easy way<footnote><para>Writing it this way suggests that there "
"are several ways of cutting a clip. This is in fact true.</para></footnote> "
"for this is to move the timeline cursor to the desired position (&ie; the "
"position where you want to cut the video), then drag the left border of the "
"clip when the resize marker appears. It will snap in at the timeline cursor "
"when you move close enough."
msgstr ""
"Ker po jedi pride igranje, je na voljo posnetek biljarda. Dodajte ga tudi na "
"časovnico. Prvih 1,5 sekunde se v posnetku ne zgodi nič, zato ga je morda "
"treba <guilabel>obrezati</guilabel> , da video ne postane dolgočasen. "
"Preprost način<footnote><para>Pisanje na ta način kaže, da obstaja več "
"načinov rezanja posnetka. To je pravzaprav res.</para></footnote> To pomeni, "
"da premaknete kazalec časovnice na želeni položaj (t.j.položaj, kjer želite "
"odrezati posnetek), nato pa povlecite levo obrobo posnetka, ko se prikaže "
"oznaka za spreminjanje velikosti. Pripne se na kazalec časovnice, ko se "
"premaknete dovolj blizu."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Overlapping clips</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prekrivajoči se posnetki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Overlapping clips</para>"
msgstr "<para>Prekrivajoči se posnetki</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a <emphasis>transition</emphasis> between eating (the Spoon) and "
"playing billiards, the two clips need to overlap. To be precise: the second "
"clip should be above or below the first one and end some frames after the "
"second one begins. Zooming in until the ticks for single frames appear helps "
"here; it also makes it easy to always have the same transition duration, "
"five frames in this case."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati <emphasis>prehod</emphasis> med jedjo (žlico) in igranjem "
"biljarda, se morata oba posnetka prekrivati. Če smo natančni: drugi posnetek "
"mora biti nad ali pod prvim in se končati nekaj sličic po začetku drugega. "
"Povečava, dokler se ne prikažejo kljukice za posamezne sličice, pomaga "
"tukaj; Prav tako omogoča enostavno vedno enako trajanje prehoda, v tem "
"primeru pet sličic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can zoom in by either using the <guilabel>zoom slider</guilabel> at the "
"bottom of the &kdenlive; window, or with <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Mousewheel</"
"keycap></keycombo>. &kdenlive; will zoom to the timeline cursor, so first "
"set it to the position which you want to see enlarged, then zoom in."
msgstr ""
"Pogled lahko povečate z <guilabel>drsnikom za povečavo</guilabel> na dnu "
"okna &kdenlive; ali s <keycombo>krmilko<keycap>kolešček miške</keycap></"
"keycombo>. &kdenlive; bo povečal kazalec časovnice, zato ga najprej "
"nastavite na položaj, ki ga želite prikazati povečano, nato pa povečajte "
"pogled."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Transition marker</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Označevalnik prehoda</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Transition marker</para>"
msgstr "<para>Označevalnik prehoda</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that the clips overlap, the transition can be added. This is done either "
"by right-clicking on the upper clip and choosing <guilabel>Add Transition</"
"guilabel> or, easier, by hovering the mouse over the lower right corner of "
"the Spoon clip until the pointing-finger pointer is shown and the message "
"<quote>Click to add transition</quote> appears. The latter, by default, adds "
"a dissolve transition, which is in this case the best idea anyway since the "
"Spoon is not required for playing."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko se posnetki prekrivajo, lahko prehod dodamo. To storite tako, da z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknete zgornji posnetek in izberete <guilabel>Dodaj "
"prehod</guilabel> ali, kar je še lažje, s kazalcem miške nad spodnjim desnim "
"kotom posnetka Spoon, dokler se ne prikaže kazalec kazalca in se prikaže "
"sporočilo <quote>Kliknite za dodajanje prehoda</quote> . Slednji privzeto "
"doda prehod preliva, kar je v tem primeru najboljša ideja, saj žlica ni "
"potrebna za igranje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dissolve transitions fades the first clip into the second one. See also "
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Transitions\">Transition section of the manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prehod preliva prelije prvi posnetek v drugega. Glejte tudi <ulink url="
"\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/Transitions"
"\">razdelek priročnika Prehod</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let’s now add the last clip, the Piano, and again apply a dissolve "
"transition. When adding it on the first track of the timeline, you need to "
"click on the new clip’s lower left edge to add the transition to the "
"previous clip."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj dodamo zadnji posnetek, klavir, in ponovno uporabimo prehod preliva. Ko "
"ga dodate na prvo stezo časovnice, morate klikniti spodnji levi rob novega "
"posnetka, da dodate prehod na prejšnji posnetek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Effects"
msgstr "Učinki"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Effect List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seznam učinkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Effect List</para>"
msgstr "<para>Seznam učinkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Piano can be colourized by adding an <emphasis>effect</emphasis> to it. "
"Select the piano clip, then double-click the <guilabel>RGB Adjustment</"
"guilabel> effect in the <guilabel>Effect List</guilabel>. If it is not "
"visible, you can get it via <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Effect List</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Klavir lahko obarvamo z dodajanjem <emphasis>učinka</emphasis>. Izberite "
"klavirski posnetek in nato dvokliknite učinek <guilabel>prilagajanja RGB</"
"guilabel> na <guilabel>seznamu učinkov</guilabel>. Če ni viden, ga lahko "
"dobite prek <menuchoice><guimenuitem>seznama učinkov</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the effect has been added, its name will be added to the timeline clip. "
"It will also be shown in the <guilabel>Properties</guilabel> widget."
msgstr ""
"Ko je učinek dodan, bo njegovo ime dodano v posnetek časovnice. Prikazana bo "
"tudi v gradniku <guilabel>Lastnosti</guilabel> ."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Effect Stack with RGB adjustment</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Sklad učinkov z nastavitvijo RGB</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Effect Stack with RGB adjustment</para>"
msgstr "<para>Sklad učinkov z nastavitvijo RGB</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a warm yellow-orange tone on the image, fitting the comfortable "
"evening, blue needs to be reduced and red and green improved."
msgstr ""
"Da bi dobili topel rumeno-oranžen ton v sliki, ki se prilega udobnemu "
"večeru, je treba modro zmanjšati in izpostaviti rdečo in zeleno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The values in the Properties widget can be changed by using the slider "
"(middle mouse button resets it to the default value), or by entering a value "
"directly by double-clicking the number to the right of the slider."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti v gradniku Lastnosti lahko spremenite z drsnikom (srednja tipka "
"miške ga ponastavi na privzeto vrednost) ali tako, da vnesete vrednost "
"neposredno tako, da dvokliknete številko desno od drsnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Properties widget always refers to the timeline clip that is currently "
"selected. Each effect can be temporarily disabled by clicking the eye icon, "
"or all effects for that clip can be disabled using the check box at the top "
"of the Properties widget (the settings are saved though), this is &eg; "
"useful for effects that require a lot of computing power, so they can be "
"disabled when editing and enabled again for rendering."
msgstr ""
"Pripomoček Lastnosti se vedno nanaša na posnetek na časovnici, ki je "
"trenutno izbran. Vsak učinek lahko začasno onemogočite tako, da kliknete "
"ikono očesa, ali pa vse učinke za ta posnetek onemogočite s potrditvenim "
"poljem na vrhu pripomočka Lastnosti (vendar so nastavitve shranjene), to je "
"npr. uporabno za učinke, ki zahtevajo veliko računalniške moči, zato jih je "
"mogoče onemogočiti med montiranjem in znova omogočiti za izrisovanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For some effects, like the one used there, it is possible to add keyframes. "
"The framed watch icon indicates this. Keyframes are used for changing effect "
"parameters over time. In our clip this allows us to fade the piano’s colour "
"from a warm evening colour to a cold night colour."
msgstr ""
"Nekaterim učinkom, kot je tisti, ki se uporablja tam, je mogoče dodati "
"ključne sličice. To označuje ikona uokvirjene ure. Ključne sličice se "
"uporabljajo za spreminjanje parametrov učinka skozi čas. V našem posnetku "
"nam to omogoča, da barvo klavirja iz tople večerne barve zbledimo v hladno "
"nočno barvo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Keyframes for effects</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ključne sličice za učinke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Keyframes for effects</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ključne sličice za učinke</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clicking the <guilabel>keyframe</guilabel> icon (the clock icon framed "
"in the previous image), the Properties widget will re-arrange. By default "
"there will be two keyframes, one at the beginning of the timeline clip and "
"one at the end. Move the timeline cursor to the end of the timeline clip, "
"such that the project monitor actually shows the new colours when changing "
"the parameters of the keyframe at the end."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete ikono <guilabel>ključne sličice</guilabel> (ikona uokvirjene ure "
"na prejšnji sliki), se pripomoček Lastnosti preuredi. Privzeto bosta na "
"voljo dve ključni sličici, ena na začetku posnetka časovnice in ena na "
"koncu. Premaknite kazalec časovnice na konec posnetka časovnice, tako da "
"ogled projekta dejansko prikaže nove barve pri spreminjanju parametrov "
"ključne sličice na koncu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure the last keyframe is selected in the Properties list. Then you are "
"ready to flood the piano with a deep blue."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali je na seznamu Lastnosti izbrana zadnja ključna sličica. Potem "
"ste pripravljeni preplaviti klavir s temno modro barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the timeline cursor to the beginning of the project and playing it "
"(with <keycap>Space</keycap>, or the <guilabel>Play</guilabel> button in the "
"<guilabel>Project Monitor</guilabel>), the piano should now change the "
"colour as desired."
msgstr ""
"Če premaknete kazalec časovnice na začetek projekta in ga predvajate (s "
"<keycap>preslednico</keycap> ali gumbom <guilabel>Predvajaj</guilabel> v "
"<guilabel>ogledu projekta</guilabel>), bi moral klavir zdaj spremeniti barvo "
"na nastavljen način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keyframing was the hardest part of this tutorial. If you managed to do it, "
"you will master &kdenlive; easily!"
msgstr ""
"Delo s ključnimi sličicami je bil najtežji del te vadnice. Če vam je to "
"uspelo, boste enostavno obvladali &kdenlive;!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Effects\">Effects section of the manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Glejte tudi <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Effects\">razdelek priročnika Učinki</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Music"
msgstr "Glasba"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Audio fadeout</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pojemanje zvoka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Audio fadeout</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pojemanje zvoka</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the clips do not provide any audio, let’s search for some nice piece "
"of music, from your local collection or on web pages like <ulink url="
"\"http://www.jamendo.com\">Jamendo</ulink>. The audio clip should, after "
"adding it, be dragged to an audio track on the timeline."
msgstr ""
"Ker posnetki ne vsebujejo nobenega zvoka, poiščimo nekaj lepe glasbe, iz "
"vaše krajevne zbirke ali na spletnih straneh, kot je <ulink url=\"http://www."
"jamendo.com\">Jamendo</ulink>. Zvočni posnetek je treba po dodajanju povleči "
"na zvočni posnetek na časovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The audio clip can be resized on the timeline the same way as video clips "
"are. The cursor will snap in at the end of the project automatically. To add "
"a fade out effect at the end of the audio clip (except if you found a file "
"with exactly the right length) you can hover the top right (or left) edge of "
"the timeline clip and drag the red shaded triangle to the position where "
"fading out should start."
msgstr ""
"Velikost zvočnega posnetka na časovnici lahko spremenite na enak način kot "
"za videoposnetke. Kazalec se bo samodejno pripel na konec projekta. Če "
"želite na konec zvočnega posnetka dodati učinek pojemanja (razen če ste "
"našli datoteko z ravno pravo dolžino), se s kazalcem miške pomaknite na "
"zgornji desni (ali levi) rob posnetka časovnice in povlecite rdeči osenčeni "
"trikotnik na mesto, kjer naj bi se začelo pojemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shaded triangle is a shorthand for adding the effect "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fade out</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Both ways lead to the same result."
msgstr ""
"Ta osenčeni trikotnik je okrajšava za dodajanje učinka, ki predstavlja "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>pojemanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>pojemanje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Oba načina vodita do istega rezultata."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rendering"
msgstr "Izrisovanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Rendering dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno izrisovanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rendering dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno izrisovanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A few minutes left, and the project is finished! Click the Render button (or "
"go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Render</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo>) to "
"get the dialog shown on the left. Select the desired output file for our new "
"video with all effects and transitions, choose MP4 (works nearly "
"everywhere), select the output file location and press the <guilabel>Render "
"to File</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Ostalo je še nekaj minut in projekt je končan! Kliknite gumb Izriši (ali "
"pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izris</guimenuitem> <guimenu>projekta</"
"guimenu></menuchoice> ali pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo>), da "
"se pogovorno okno prikaže na levi strani. Izberite želeno izhodno datoteko "
"za naš novi video z vsemi učinki in prehodi, izberite MP4 (deluje skoraj "
"povsod), izberite mesto izhodne datoteke in pritisnite gumb <guilabel>Izriši "
"v datoteko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Rendering progress</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredek izrisovanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rendering progress</para>"
msgstr "<para>Napredek izrisovanja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After some seconds rendering will be finished, and your first &kdenlive; "
"project completed. Congratulations!"
msgstr ""
"Po nekaj sekundah bo izrisovanje končano in vaš prvi projekt &kdenlive; je "
"dokončan. Čestitamo!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Complete manual"
msgstr "Celoten priročnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Further documentation for the current version of &kdenlive; can be found in "
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual"
"\">the full manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatna dokumentacija za trenutno različico &kdenlive; najdete v <ulink url="
"\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual\">celovitem "
"priročniku</ulink>."

