"org/index.php?title=Kdenlive/Manual/QuickStart&amp;action=history\">Kdenlive/"
"Manual/QuickStart page history</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Dokumentacija: Avtorske pravice, glejte zgodovino strani UserBase <ulink url="
"\"http://userbase.kde.org/index.php?title=Kdenlive/Manual/QuickStart&amp;"
"action=history\">Kdenlive/Manual/QuickStart</ulink>."

